# Phase React-2: SEO Optimization for React Version

**Purpose:** Implement comprehensive SEO optimizations for the React SPA version of Neera Sarees, focusing on meta tags, structured data, content structure, and discoverability. The primary goal is to optimize the "All Sarees" page (`/products`) as the main product landing page while ensuring all page types have proper SEO foundations.

**Target Outcome:** Significantly improved search engine visibility and rankings through proper meta tags, structured data (schema markup), semantic HTML, breadcrumbs, sitemap, and optimized content structure—all without any visual design changes.

**Critical Constraints:**
- ⚠️ **ZERO VISUAL/DESIGN CHANGES** - All optimizations must be invisible to users. No layout modifications, styling changes, or new visual elements.
- ⚠️ **NO IMAGE FORMAT CHANGES** - Do not convert images to webp, avif, or any other format. Keep all image formats as-is (.jpg, .jpeg, .png).
- ⚠️ **NO LAZY LOADING CHANGES** - Do not modify existing image lazy loading behavior.
- ⚠️ **PRIMARY TARGET** - The "All Sarees" page (`/products`) is the highest priority for optimization (sitemap priority 1.0).

