## Step 6: Implement Breadcrumb Navigation

**Objective:** Add breadcrumb navigation to improve internal linking and user experience without disrupting layout.

**Actions:**

1. Create Breadcrumb component `src/components/Breadcrumb.jsx`:
   ```jsx
   import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';
   
   export default function Breadcrumb({ items }) {
     return (
       <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" className="breadcrumb-container">
         <ol className="breadcrumb-list">
           {items.map((item, index) => (
             <li key={index} className="breadcrumb-item">
               {index < items.length - 1 ? (
                 <>
                   <Link to={item.path} className="breadcrumb-link">
                     {item.name}
                   </Link>
                   <span className="breadcrumb-separator" aria-hidden="true"> / </span>
                 </>
               ) : (
                 <span className="breadcrumb-current" aria-current="page">
                   {item.name}
                 </span>
               )}
             </li>
           ))}
         </ol>
       </nav>
     );
   }
   ```
