## Step 7: Generate Sitemap & Configure Robots.txt

**Objective:** Create XML sitemap with all URLs and configure robots.txt to guide search engine crawling. Prioritize All Sarees page as primary target.

**Actions:**

1. Create sitemap generation script `scripts/generate-sitemap.js`:
   - Fetch all products from Supabase
   - Generate URLs for:
     - Homepage: `/`
     - All Sarees: `/products` (priority: 1.0, changefreq: daily)
     - Each product: `/products/{fabric}/{slug}` (priority: 0.8)
     - Each fabric category: `/fabric/{fabric}` (priority: 0.7)
     - Each print category: `/prints/{print}` (priority: 0.7)
     - Key pages: `/contact-us`, `/privacy-policy`, `/terms`, `/story` (priority: 0.5)
   - Example script structure:
   ```js
   import { createClient } from '@supabase/supabase-js';
   import fs from 'fs';
   
   const supabase = createClient(
     process.env.VITE_SUPABASE_URL,
     process.env.VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY
   );
   
   async function generateSitemap() {
     const { data: products } = await supabase
       .from('products')
       .select('fabric_type, slug, updated_at');
     
     const fabricTypes = [...new Set(products.map(p => p.fabric_type))];
     const printTypes = [...new Set(products.map(p => p.print_type))];
     
     let sitemap = '<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>\n';
     sitemap += '<urlset xmlns="http://www.sitemaps.org/schemas/sitemap/0.9">\n';
     
     // Homepage
     sitemap += '  <url>\n';
     sitemap += '    <loc>https://neera.store/</loc>\n';
     sitemap += '    <changefreq>weekly</changefreq>\n';
     sitemap += '    <priority>0.9</priority>\n';
     sitemap += '  </url>\n';
     
     // All Sarees page (HIGHEST PRIORITY)
     sitemap += '  <url>\n';
     sitemap += '    <loc>https://neera.store/products</loc>\n';
     sitemap += '    <changefreq>daily</changefreq>\n';
     sitemap += '    <priority>1.0</priority>\n';
     sitemap += '  </url>\n';
     
     // Product pages
     products.forEach(product => {
       sitemap += '  <url>\n';
       sitemap += `    <loc>https://neera.store/products/${product.fabric_type}/${product.slug}</loc>\n`;
       sitemap += '    <changefreq>weekly</changefreq>\n';
       sitemap += '    <priority>0.8</priority>\n';
       sitemap += '  </url>\n';
     });
     
     // Fabric categories
     fabricTypes.forEach(fabric => {
       sitemap += '  <url>\n';
       sitemap += `    <loc>https://neera.store/fabric/${fabric}</loc>\n`;
       sitemap += '    <changefreq>weekly</changefreq>\n';
       sitemap += '    <priority>0.7</priority>\n';
       sitemap += '  </url>\n';
     });
     
     // Print categories
     printTypes.forEach(print => {
       sitemap += '  <url>\n';
       sitemap += `    <loc>https://neera.store/prints/${print}</loc>\n`;
       sitemap += '    <changefreq>weekly</changefreq>\n';
       sitemap += '    <priority>0.7</priority>\n';
       sitemap += '  </url>\n';
     });
     
     // Key pages
     const keyPages = [
       { path: '/contact-us', priority: 0.5 },
       { path: '/privacy-policy', priority: 0.3 },
       { path: '/terms', priority: 0.3 },
       { path: '/story', priority: 0.6 }
     ];
     
     keyPages.forEach(page => {
       sitemap += '  <url>\n';
       sitemap += `    <loc>https://neera.store${page.path}</loc>\n`;
       sitemap += '    <changefreq>monthly</changefreq>\n';
       sitemap += `    <priority>${page.priority}</priority>\n`;
       sitemap += '  </url>\n';
     });
     
     sitemap += '</urlset>';
     
     fs.writeFileSync('./public/sitemap.xml', sitemap);
     console.log('✅ Sitemap generated successfully');
     console.log(`   Total URLs: ${products.length + fabricTypes.length + printTypes.length + keyPages.length + 2}`);
   }
   
   generateSitemap();
   ```
2. Run sitemap generation:
   - Execute: `node scripts/generate-sitemap.js`
   - Verify `public/sitemap.xml` created
   - Open file and verify:
     - Valid XML format
     - All Sarees page has priority 1.0
     - All expected URLs present
     - Proper structure
3. Create or update `public/robots.txt`:
   ```
   User-agent: *
   Allow: /
   
   Sitemap: https://neera.store/sitemap.xml
   ```
4. Verify sitemap accessibility in dev server:
   - Start server: `npm run dev`
   - Navigate to: `http://localhost:5173/sitemap.xml`
   - Verify sitemap displays in browser
   - Navigate to: `http://localhost:5173/robots.txt`
   - Verify robots.txt displays
5. Count URLs in sitemap:
   - Expected: ~137 products + fabric categories + print categories + key pages
   - Should be 150+ total URLs
   - Document count in PROGRESS.md
6. Verify All Sarees page priority:
   - Open `public/sitemap.xml`
   - Find `/products` URL
   - Verify `<priority>1.0</priority>`
   - Verify `<changefreq>daily</changefreq>`
7. Test sitemap with online validator:
   - Use: https://www.xml-sitemaps.com/validate-xml-sitemap.html
   - Or Google Search Console (if site already submitted)
   - Document validation results
8. Document in PROGRESS.md:
   - Script created: `scripts/generate-sitemap.js`
   - Sitemap generated: `public/sitemap.xml`
   - Total URLs: [count]
   - All Sarees priority: 1.0 (confirmed)
   - robots.txt configured: Yes
   - Files accessible in dev server: Verified
   - Validation results: [summary]

